txt.en: You have defeated many Dead in Tarlang's Crown.
You have defeated many of the Dead in Tarlang's Crown. They may never truly find rest under the Heirs of Castamir, but you have done well to purge the Crown of their frightful forms.
Defeat Ruthless Warriors in Tarlang's Crown ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
You have defeated many of the Dead in Tarlang's Crown. Although their curse shall bring them forth once more, you have greatly weakened the forces in Tarlang's Crown, albeit temporarily.
Drawn to Tarlang's Crown by Azruthor, the Ruthless Dead now strike fear into the enemies of the Heirs of Castamir.

Defeated Ruthless Oathbreakers in Tarlang's Crown ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

While searching for leader of the Dead that Gondren mentioned, you have encountered many other grim Oathbreakers in Tarlang's Crown. The fear these cursed Men could strike into the people of Gondor is unknowable, and would break many Gondorian forces before the Corsairs even drew their blades.\n\nIf victory is to be won against Azruthor and his forces in Tarlang's Crown, they must be put to rest, even if only for a short while.
Defeat Ruthless Oathbreakers in Tarlang's Crown ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
The Dead can be found throughout Tarlang's Crown.\n\nYou have encountered the Ruthless Dead and should defeat them before they can be wielded against the people of Gondor.
